title: Offseason Drivetrain
author: Nick
description:
Just a drivetrain I made during the offseason between In to the Deep and Decode. 

Current feature include:

-Belted Mecanum powered by 4 GoBilda Motors
-Wheel Cover and Motor Mounts designed for 3D printing
-Vertical and Horizontal linear slide mounts (Misumi 230s)
-Control and Expansion Hub mounting
-GoBilda 4-Bar Odometry mounting

Features I want to add:

-Spools and Motor Mounts for Slides
-PTO
-Better Motor Mounting
-Robot Sign (would like to use dovetail joints for flush design.)
